game.name: 100 Speed Bumps Challenge Simulation
game.description:
Have you ever imagined what would happen in case if you dared to drive more than 100 speed bumps at over 100 miles per hour? If not, join 100 Speed Bumps Challenge Simulation and get ready to try it out in this realistic car racing challenge. There are different supercars available to test on bumps over 100 speed. This brand new racing game will instantly take you to an environment where you have to put your driving skills to challenge. The safety and protection of your car will depend on the speed bumps. 

Control the speed of your car using the speed breakers, which also hinder your vehicle from being destroyed on the speed bumps. Join the real car simulation fun to enjoy the best ever car race experience in this speed breaker game! Here you will also learn how to drive safely on the speed breakers and speed bumps. Try to maintain your high speed while driving your vehicle on more than 100 bumps! Many car race lovers want to play this free online car simulation game because of wanting a breaking from other car games. 

Remember, the good suspensions are sufficient enough to make your driving experience amazing no matter how fast you hit speed bumps or speed breakers. Try to not let your high speed car go off the road to reach it safely to its destination to ensure your win in the end of this cool HTML5 car game! Different tracks and levels with 100 bumps and multiple luxury vehicles combined with the attractive sounds and amazing high resolution graphics will keep you busy for hours. Drive your car using Arrows/WASD and change view by using C!
